Module jakarta.persistence
Package jakarta.persistence

Annotation Interface PostPersist

@Target(METHOD) @Retention(RUNTIME) public @interface PostPersist
Specifies a callback method for the corresponding lifecycle event. This annotation may be applied to methods of an entity class, a mapped superclass, or a callback listener class.

Any generated primary key value is available when this callback occurs.

1.0
